ch baked cheese cake.  Bake 5 minutes at 400°F. or in 325°F. convection oven 3 minutes on low fan, open vent.  Follow Step 10.\n7.  CHEESE CAKE WITH STRAWBERRY GLAZE TOPPING:  Follow Steps 1 through 9.  Prepare 1 recipe Strawberry Glaze Topping.  Spread 4 lb 11 oz (7½ cups) topping over each chilled cake.  For Variation 2, spread about 11½ oz (1-1/8 cups) topping over each chilled pie.\n8.  CHEESE CAKE WITH BLUEBERRY TOPPING (CHEESE CAKE MIX):  Omit Steps 1 through 9.  Prepare Cheese Cake Variation1.  Use 8 lb 12 oz (3-3/4 qt - 1¼ No.10 cn) canned prepared blueberry pie filling.  In Step 10, spread 4 lb 6 oz (7½ cups) filling over each chilled cake.  For Variation 2, spread about 10½ oz (1-1/8 cups) filling over each chilled pie.	2023-10-13 13:40:40.780786	2023-10-13 13:40:40.780786
