t.\n2.  HOT ROLLS (ROLL MIX):  Omit Steps 1 through 5.  Use 15-lb (3-1/3 No.10 cn) Roll Mix, 5-oz (1 cup) active dry yeast and 3-1/2 cups water.  Prepare dough according to instructions on container.  Follow Steps 6 through 10.\n3.  OATMEAL ROLLS:  Follow Steps 1 and 2.  In Step 3, reduce flour to 8-lb (2 gal); add 4-lb 4-oz (1½ qt) rolled oats.  Proceed with remainder of Step 3.  Follow Steps 4 through 9.  In Step 10, bake 20 to 25 minutes or for convection oven, see Step 10.\n	2023-10-13 13:40:40.780786	2023-10-13 13:40:40.780786
